<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="V" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Virginal" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Virginal,</orth> adj. maidenly: <cit><quote>tears v.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 5.2.52" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B V, 2, 52</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the v. palms of your daughters,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 5.2.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. V, 2, 45</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>without any more v. fencing,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 4.6.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 6, 62</bibl></cit>.
